reviewText: Just wanted to say that my grandaughter is so taken with anything that Elmo does that at 18m she is so brilliant, LOL. she is enamored with Elmo so anytime we get something of his especially dvd's that she can watch, they are very affective. reviewText: This is our favorite Elmo's World DVD. Featuring 20 mins of each: UP/DOWN, OPEN/CLOSE and FAST/SLOW (Plays for a straight hour, not 3 separate sections you have to select each time). Definitely a winner and not as annoying as other episodes. We love it.

reviewText: I absolutely LOVE LOVE Elmo! Very entertaining, cute and educational. My son is 1 and keeps repeating what elmo says. The video is around 50 minutes so you don't have to finish the whole thing in one shot cuz their attention span is only 10 minutes or so. But i put it on for him every day!
